-- Argentina Loses Appeal on Bondholder Payment Formula
-- B y   B o b   V a n   V o r i s
-- 2013-08-23T13:40:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-23/appeals-court-rejects-argentina-s-formula-for-paying-bonds.html
Argentina’s proposed formula for
paying holders of its defaulted debt was rejected by a U.S.
appeals court, ruling in the country’s decade-long attempt to
avoid paying creditors after a 2001 financial crisis.  To contact the reporter on this story:
